Class AbstractDocumentTemplateAsync

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jnosql.artemis.document.AbstractDocumentTemplateAsync
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentTemplateAsync

    public abstract class AbstractDocumentTemplateAsync
extends Object
implements DocumentTemplateAsync
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the DocumentTemplateAsync interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
